article_title: Kids, parents frolic at Davis Islands pool’s reopening
article_text: Hillsborough, Tampa, 8-23-14---The newly reopened Roy Jenkins Pool on Davis Islands was a popular spot on Saturady as the pool was opened to the public with no admission as paert of the grand opening. ANDY JONES/STAFF
